body.p:
supports several media types, allowing you to set different styles for presenting a document on different media (on the screen, on paper and so on). The following media types are supported:
screen - the styles marked with this media type are used only for rendering a document in the Author mode;
all - the styles marked with this media type are used for rendering a document in the Author mode and also for printing the document;
oxygen - the styles marked with this media type are used only for rendering a document in the Author mode;This is an specific media.
print - the styles marked with this media type are used only for printing a document.
